        Creates a new ICMP Echo Request message.
        Parameters:
        src_addr - IP source address
        dst_addr - IP destination address
        id - identifier to aid in matching echos and replies (may be zero)
        sqn - sequence number to aid in matching echos and replies (may be zero)
        echo_data - the data to be included in the ICMP message
